{"tid":1276340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】律師會會長  譴責衝擊立法會大樓 冀警方嚴正執法","createTime":"2019-07-02T02:39:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T06:08:57.000Z","uid":142878,"like":3,"dislike":74,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"bfbf9ce3260457eadfe462402b5706762ca849d9","tid":1276340,"uid":142878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:39:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1534888\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1534888&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2BjH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=43e6cdfc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1534888&h=c2cbfb3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1534888</a><br />\n<br />\n示威者在7月1日衝擊立法會大樓，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港律師會會長彭韻僖表示，衝擊立法會的行為嚴重破壞香港法治，示威者應受到譴責，冀警方嚴正執法，示威者停止違法行為。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n她表示，衝擊立法會的場面令很多人感到痛心，並非平時所見的香港，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>認為這種暴力方法表達意見完全不能接受</strong></span>，無助解決問題。她表示，示威者的訴求非常清楚，相信政府會溝通和聆聽意見，但示威者必須先冷靜下來，不能以這種失去理性的狀態解決問題。她希望，每個香港市民，包括法律界人士，都能夠盡一份力維護香港法治。"},{"pid":"45fd899dad93b7e802cdfb8e4643980a514ee68a","tid":1276340,"uid":41298,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:40:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd85c5517d3c1ecd97f0e8f9ba8b864f02447c82","tid":1276340,"uid":121255,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:40:17.000Z","msg":"示威者的訴求非常清楚，相信政府會溝通和聆聽意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd0abaf7e2fb8fb9c526cd27a9a21f1e8143cc5","tid":1276340,"uid":142878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:40:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/346950/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2F346950%2F&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2BjH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=4a8eed0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/社會新聞/346950/</a><br />\n<br />\n律師會會長彭韻僖晚上亦表示，衝擊並毀壞立法會的行為，令香港的法治受到破壞，認為示威者的暴力行為必須受到譴責。另外彭希望警方能盡快嚴厲執法，保護香港的財產、秩序及安寧。<br />\n<br />\n彭韻僖又稱，法治是香港的核心價值，每個人對法治都有責任，希望大家都守護法治。法治不單單是律師和法官所關心的，也是所有香港人所關心的。"},{"pid":"2ac455ceb0710ffabe483e956d8552b726de1337","tid":1276340,"uid":19126,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:41:05.000Z","msg":"法律面前，窮人含撚，有得傾既洗唔洗衝呀屌你老母，你咁叻你出聲明叫政府傾呀笨柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5702fa749815f2045ad467d34bf2124db1805ad","tid":1276340,"uid":20602,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:41:30.000Z","msg":"阿會長分唔分到法治同法律分別？"},{"pid":"c6b2913e70b036ea561a9dad1bf18ac6d1fddde6","tid":1276340,"uid":147434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bfbf9ce3260457eadfe462402b5706762ca849d9","tid":1276340,"uid":142878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T02:39:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1534888\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1534888&d=nd52c%2FRhS%2BUv0SpwCnLJ%2BjH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=43e6cdfc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1534888&h=c2cbfb3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1534888</a><br />\n<br />\n示威者在7月1日衝擊立法會大樓，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港律師會會長彭韻僖表示，衝擊立法會的行為嚴重破壞香港法治，示威者應受到譴責，冀警方嚴正執法，示威者停止違法行為。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n她表示，衝擊立法會的場面令很多人感到痛心，並非平時所見的香港，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>認為這種暴力方法表達意見完全不能接受</strong></span>，無助解決問題。她表示，示威者的訴求非常清楚，相信政府會溝通和聆聽意見，但示威者必須先冷靜下來，不能以這種失去理性的狀態解決問題。她希望，每個香港市民，包括法律界人士，都能夠盡一份力維護香港法治。"},"citedBy":0,"replyT